Vue Tab Complete Input

A tab completable <input> component for Vue.js

View Docs and Examples

# Demo

# Install

yarn add vue-tab-complete-input

# Include

<tab-complete-input v-model="text" :data-source="list" />

<script>
import TabCompleteInput from "vue-tab-complete-input"

export default {
  components: {
    TabCompleteInput
  },
  data() {
    return {
      list: [],
      text: ''
    }
  },
}
</script>
